    "37 Soper (2020).",
    "38 Tan (2020).",
    "The researchers then have the option of either (i) relying on pre-trained word embeddings (based on the training done by their developers) such as word2vec trained on the Google News corpus, 39 or (ii) training the embeddings themselves to make sure that they assign numerical values based on their specific dataset/research topic -so that they can be used on later NLP tasks with greater accuracy."
